summary:
SUPPLY CHAIN- SALES - CLIENTSERVICE- MARKETING- LANGUAGES ( native Italian / English / Spanish / Dutch )

I am a young and motivated hard worker, client oriented and focused on details.
I have a natural inclination for sales,  I am commercial minded and used to an international environment. In my past job experiences I learned how to deal with customers, how to work for their satisfaction and I develop a good problem-solving attitude..
I gain a lot of knowledge also from my job experiences in the tourism industry and I am use to work with people from different countries and cultures.
I like working in a team, but I also enjoy to be an independent worker, as well as I have leadership capacities. I am flexible and I love challenges. Representativeness and good presence are also in my personal background.
